# Sculptural Luxury Minimal: Source of Truth

> **Design Philosophy:** The website is a gallery. The product is the sculpture.

This document serves as the definitive guide for creating ultra-high-end fashion e-commerce sites inspired by the **Maison Alaïa** aesthetic, with references to **Balenciaga** and **Celine**. Every design decision, component specification, and interaction pattern is documented here to ensure consistency across implementations.

