#### Slow Zoom Effect

**Behavior:** On hover, the product image zooms in slowly, revealing texture and detail.

**Implementation:**
```css
.product-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transform: scale(1);
  transition: transform 0.6s ease-out;
}

.product-card:hover .product-image {
  transform: scale(1.1); /* 10% zoom */
}
```

**Variations:**
- **Subtle Zoom:** `scale(1.05)` (5% zoom)
- **Medium Zoom:** `scale(1.1)` (10% zoom)
- **Strong Zoom:** `scale(1.15)` (15% zoom) — use sparingly

**Combined with Image Swap:**
```css
/* Zoom + Image Swap */
.product-image-container {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.product-image {
  transform: scale(1);
  transition: transform 0.6s ease-out, opacity 0.4s ease-in-out;
}

.product-card:hover .product-image {
  transform: scale(1.1);
  opacity: 0;
}

.product-card:hover .product-image-secondary {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: scale(1.1);
}
```

